metadata.name: Alpha Wave Visions NFT Collection: The Spiral #1
metadata.description: A collection of Audio-reactive generative art revealing the visions of those who tried the Alpha Wave Experience. Entangled in a colourful spiral. This animation will give you intense hallucinations. Create the experience yourself. Look at the visual then look at another computer screen it will move. Created by Alpha Wave Experience art collective. Generative Art: Dimitri Thouzery. Music: Toga Fidan / Dan Ghenacia
